		<h3 style="margin-top: 20px;">Background</h3>
	    <div class="Paragraph">
		    <p>
			    Moto Professional is a service offered by the Media Panther Network (MPN), which aims to revolutionise the motorsports media industry by
			    providing a quick, simple, and easy to use self-service way to purchase the best motorsports photography available, online, whether you're an Editor, 
			    Event Organiser, Racer, Manager, etc. A business-to-business service at the moment, MPN plans on providing general-public services in the near future.
		    </p>
		    <p>
			    Initially covering the British Superbikes, British MX, World MX racing series' and the UK rounds of the World Superbikes and MotoGP series', we offer
			    a huge range of the best racing photographs. Though we're not limited to just racing, with coverage of other motorcycle events such as shows, launches and other motorcycle events.
		    </p>
		    <p>
			    The idea behind Moto Professional is to allow people in the industry who do not want to, or are not able to commission an agency to shoot for them. By us not comitting to
			    to shooting a specific client, we are able to capture a huge range of subjects with our distinctive style and then give you the convinience to browse our collections at your discretion. We're already
			    shooting thousands of bikes, people and events every week, so this way you get a service not offered elsewhere. Simplicity is key here.
		    </p>
		</div>
